---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Solut Enerji | Güneş Enerjisi ve EV Şarj Çözümleri"
  description="Yüksek mühendislik standartları ile güneşten gelen gücü yaşam alanlarınıza ve ulaşımınıza entegre ediyoruz."
>
<!-- Hero Section: The Kinetic Monolith -->
<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center pt-20 overflow-hidden bg-primary">
<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-40">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="Industrial solar panel farm under clear blue sky" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBLsEE338Ym0CXCfZP7R9qSI4axDQ3zHfu6Ym0h7WOKgXjnOevL78_3DwZZQOKjP7XK25Zi2K2YE9feYdvVyJG3A_S0indL-oY1vqEmhmhiU2O1roe7YgrIzASwduSaRAc-o_s7P0ElGiMD3Emxo10CVgiPqMWqPRCewdIp8iZLoR0GUWreg5gCPuTDqcsJ2MFIiOrQz6FmPeWKIt9jZAvf4YKF8KlgPt4LjxBjxnrbAOCvHWWSOSmcLpPI9bUgg1iVHVPkfIO3ZKA">
</div>
<div class="absolute inset-0 z-10 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary via-primary/80 to-transparent"></div>
<div class="relative z-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
<div class="lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center">
<span class="label-md uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-secondary-container font-semibold mb-6">Enerji Sistemleri Mühendisliği</span>
<h1 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white leading-[1.1] tracking-tighter mb-8">
                    Güneş. Çözüm.<br><span class="text-secondary-container">Solut.</span>
</h1>
<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-primary-fixed-dim font-body max-w-xl mb-10 leading-relaxed">
                    Yüksek mühendislik standartları ile güneşten gelen gücü yaşam alanlarınıza ve ulaşımınıza entegre ediyoruz.
                </p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
<button class="bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-fixed px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold text-base hover:opacity-90 transition-all flex items-center gap-2">
<span>Çözümlerimizi Keşfedin</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
</button>
<a href="/iletisim/" class="border border-white/20 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold text-base hover:bg-white/20 transition-all">Hızlı Teklif Al</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="lg:col-span-5 hidden lg:flex items-center justify-center">
<div class="relative w-full aspect-[4/5]">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-4/5 h-4/5 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl z-10">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="Modern electric vehicle charging station in a clean environment" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCg4WOnrzE5SYlmHzt447I-a-SbykW4Mw0jufP_8O9mcE5IH2yKzpIVb85Iw5vOefh87vhnKrusfiKDiSqs905atGAR2FbcG3vLZkNb2V2tDwMbBx8JtEstrUA3KRDCv5mGPzHLzFzVoDzd9PkQ1klZJvYxdjGD6QoasghRW8-PLbE6VYNPYavG7yf-Lf5zpPco_d_fbxNjS8QzLm3NBI7Xs0m92YBG-IE-fRFcN1nGdp44581rJFp_2eO-OmOBbioNjTNho1IMirg">
</div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-3/5 h-3/5 rounded-xl border-8 border-primary bg-primary-container overflow-hidden shadow-2xl z-20">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="Rooftop solar panel installation close up" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA5yiH9xs-qWBr3GO2ldNHS9yhc11FZMZKJ12krivJFQkOinKJPxYmeMC-0I6e7zgXF9v7GSf8bVD4Rhf7I6NuKgkRm7i046KqpulC1w6APqOt5gUNS05mP4cuDvMKq1NJ5-c5znwqxLD7blI5JdS53pdyMsRpAfQK6QbvvlXR2IewQ7juWSPrHVzChHqD8tX8pXu4a4Fhh55P2M5mNCbGVVLVB3rkRVIqdpfCR7v4gX1XNHJGgg8lzR389VQDRJ_nNuhc5g4IOe0Y">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Services Section: Bento Grid Layout -->
<section class="py-24 px-6 bg-surface-container-low">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="mb-16">
<span class="text-secondary font-bold tracking-widest text-sm uppercase">Hizmetlerimiz</span>
<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mt-4 tracking-tight">Enerji Dönüşümünde <br>Tam Kapsamlı Çözümler</h2>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<!-- Service 1 -->
<div class="group bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-surface-container-high relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full">
<div class="text-secondary-container mb-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">solar_power</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Mesken Çatı GES Kurulumu</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-grow">
                        Evinizi kendi enerji santralinize dönüştürün. Mühendislikten kuruluma anahtar teslim çözümlerle enerji faturalarınızı sıfırlayın.
                    </p>
<a class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold hover:gap-4 transition-all" href="/gunes-enerjisi/">
<span>Detayları İncele</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">trending_flat</span>
</a>
</div>
<!-- Service 2 -->
<div class="group bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-surface-container-high relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full">
<div class="text-secondary-container mb-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">ev_charger</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Elektrikli Araç Şarj Çözümleri</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-grow">
                        AC ve DC hızlı şarj istasyonları ile hem bireysel hem de kurumsal filolarınız için kesintisiz mobilite altyapısı kuruyoruz.
                    </p>
<a class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold hover:gap-4 transition-all" href="/ev-sarj-ve-danismanlik/">
<span>Detayları İncele</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">trending_flat</span>
</a>
</div>
<!-- Service 3 -->
<div class="group bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-surface-container-high relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full">
<div class="text-secondary-container mb-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">engineering</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">GES Danışmanlık Hizmetleri</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-grow">
                        Yatırım analizi, fizibilite raporları ve teknik denetim süreçlerinde uzman mühendis kadromuzla risklerinizi minimize ediyoruz.
                    </p>
<a class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold hover:gap-4 transition-all" href="/ev-sarj-ve-danismanlik/">
<span>Detayları İncele</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">trending_flat</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Trust/Stats Section -->
<section class="py-24 px-6 bg-white overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
<div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
<div class="relative">
<div class="bg-secondary-container absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-24 h-24 rounded-full z-0 opacity-20"></div>
<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary relative z-10 leading-tight">
                        Rakamlarla Solut Enerji <br>Güvencesi
                    </h2>
<p class="mt-6 text-on-surface-variant text-lg leading-relaxed">
                        Yılların tecrübesi ve yüzlerce başarılı proje ile Türkiye'nin enerji dönüşümüne öncülük ediyoruz.
                    </p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
<div>
<div class="font-headline text-5xl font-black text-primary">500+</div>
<div class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary mt-2">Tamamlanan Proje</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="font-headline text-5xl font-black text-primary">12MW+</div>
<div class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary mt-2">Kurulu Güç</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="font-headline text-5xl font-black text-primary">99%</div>
<div class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary mt-2">Müşteri Memnuniyeti</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="font-headline text-5xl font-black text-primary">24/7</div>
<div class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary mt-2">Teknik Destek</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative">
<div class="bg-surface-container rounded-3xl p-4 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
<img class="rounded-2xl w-full h-[450px] object-cover" data-alt="Professional engineers reviewing energy system blueprints" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDJmz9PyFKBk46eG2SXqAshAHV1O56k44mvhK5_EH33ukaj4pdQzul0_Z5IvdEO0nwIqbKn7tP2dx1q-1XpdRprMe3z3Gj14qP1RDg0iWsY71Q-CHtHGM3YrbvQ9Ld3dLieSwL8KbYVkkhLvdCrciv0pqK6-BbDqCyIAeukZXMPNHmjVHxwuYB1mLGo6aXTsRMemgh4NCD18tmIQIoI6AVlW-2isUTx3GDTaplCSKuyk-BspToHHAxHSYrTOiwBu166XL6GlByvdiA">
<div class="absolute bottom-10 -left-10 bg-primary p-8 rounded-xl shadow-xl max-w-xs hidden lg:block">
<p class="text-white italic font-body">"Solut Enerji ile yaptığımız iş birliği sayesinde fabrikamızın enerji maliyetlerini %70 oranında düşürdük."</p>
<p class="text-secondary-container font-bold mt-4">— Sanayi Kuruluşu CEO'su</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Final CTA Section -->
<section class="py-20 px-6">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto kinetic-monolith-gradient rounded-[2rem] p-12 md:p-20 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-white/5 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-32 h-32 bg-secondary-container/10 rounded-full translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2"></div>
<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8 relative z-10">Kendi Enerjinizi Üretmeye <br>Hemen Başlayın</h2>
<p class="text-primary-fixed-dim text-lg mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto relative z-10">
                Uzman mühendislerimiz size en uygun çözümü sunmak için hazır. Ücretsiz keşif ve analiz için formumuzu doldurun.
            </p>
<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center relative z-10">
<a href="/iletisim/" class="bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-fixed px-10 py-5 rounded-md font-bold text-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-all active:scale-95">Ücretsiz Danışmanlık Al</a>
<a href="/iletisim/" class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md text-white border border-white/20 px-10 py-5 rounded-md font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition-all">Bize Ulaşın</a>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
